snippet.title: LISA: The Joyful - Arkantos (Mod Teaser)
snippet.description:
Music: The Big Girl has Cometh (sped up to 150%)
Note: I'm still working on this mod, so things may change (this is a collection of recordings form various versions)
First time making a teaser, so it's shit. Yeah, this is the teaser for a mod I'm working on. Also the mod is a lot better than I made it look in the trailer. Feel free to ask any questions.
LISA trilogy by Austin Jorgensen
Bundled with a mod by Pruf and BKD (from 4chan/vg)
